race.comment: ZOCKETMAN (6) resumes. Went back from the awkward gate on debut before rounding them up effortlessly for a slick win over 1000m at Muswellbrook. Not asked to do much in two trials and will prove hard to stop again with the blinkers applied. ROTHO BRO (3) away only fairly on resumption when a sound fifth over 1000m at Muswellbrook. Bullock sticks and the extra trip will help his cause. EAGLES BEWARE (1) Capitalist colt who was anchored with the 59kg first-up when a fading fifth over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Well drawn and the cross-over nose band and ear muffs go on. Top three contender. IRON FURY (2) resumes today following a recent trial at Newcastle, can figure in the finish.
